data.name: instructionsLabel.Text
data.value:
How To Play Fruit Ninja?
You will have a target on the screen, this is where you're cutting.
You have to hit as many fruits as possible, you'll have 3 lives.
Hitting a bomb or missing a fruit will remove 1 life.
Each fruit you hit adds 1 point.
Your score and high score are in the top.
Player 2 can shoot bombs every 10 seconds.
